rlanguage-link-target"><span>Русский</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sq mw-list-item"><a href="https://sq.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shk%C3%ABmbimi_i_popullsis%C3%AB_midis_Greqis%C3%AB_dhe_Turqis%C3%AB" title="Shkëmbimi i popullsisë midis Greqisë dhe Turqisë – Albanian" lang="sq" hreflang="sq" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Shqip</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-simple mw-list-item"><a href="https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/Population_exchange_between_Greece_and_Turkey" title="Population exchange between Greece and Turkey – Simple English" lang="en-simple" hreflang="en-simple" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Simple English</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sr mw-list-item"><a href="https://sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A0%D0%B0%D0%B7%D0%BC%D1%98%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B0_%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%88%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B0_%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%92%D1%83_%D0%93%D1%80%D1%87%D0%BA%D0%B5_%D0%B8_%D0%A2%D1%83%D1%80%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B5" title="Размјена становништва између Грчке и Турске – Serbian" lang="sr" hreflang="sr" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Српски / srpski</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fi mw-list-item"><a href="https://fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kreikan_ja_Turkin_v%C3%A4est%C3%B6nvaihto" title="Kreikan ja Turkin väestönvaihto – Finnish" lang="fi" hreflang="fi" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Suomi</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-tr mw-list-item"><a href="https://tr.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C3%BCrkiye-Yunanistan_n%C3%BCfus_m%C3%BCbadelesi" title="Türkiye-Yunanistan nüfus mübadelesi – Turkish" lang="tr" hreflang="tr" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Türkçe</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-uk mw-list-item"><a href="https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%93%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BA%D0%BE-%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86%D1%8C%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9_%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%BC%D1%96%D0%BD_%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D1%8F%D0%BC_1923" title="Греко-турецький обмін населенням 1923 – Ukrainian" lang="uk" hreflang="uk" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Українська</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-diq mw-list-item"><a href="https://diq.wikipedia.org/wiki/V%C4%B1rnay%C4%B1%C5%9F%C3%AA_n%C4%B1fus%C3%AA_T%C4%B1rkiya-Yunan%C4%B1stani" title="Vırnayışê nıfusê Tırkiya-Yunanıstani – Zazaki" lang="diq" hreflang="diq" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Zazaki</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-zh mw-list-item"><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%8C%E8%87%98%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%BA%92%E6%8F%9B" title="希臘土耳其人口互換 – Chinese" lang="zh" hreflang="zh" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>中文</span></a></li>
			</ul>
