<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFFaulkenberry2012" class="citation thesis cs1">Faulkenberry, Jason B. (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://apps.dtic.mil/sti/pdfs/ADA563125.pdf"><i>The 1923 Greco-Turkish Population Exchange: Successful Prevention of Genocide and Mass Atrocities</i></a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> (Master's thesis). <a href="/wiki/United_States_Army_Command_and_General_Staff_College" title="United States Army Command and General Staff College">United States Army Command and General Staff College</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Adissertation&amp;rft.title=The+1923+Greco-Turkish+Population+Exchange%3A+Successful+Prevention+of+Genocide+and+Mass+Atrocities&amp;rft.degree=Master%27s&amp;rft.inst=United+States+Army+Command+and+General+Staff+College&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.aulast=Faulkenberry&amp;rft.aufirst=Jason+B.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.dtic.mil%2Fsti%2Fpdfs%2FADA563125.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APopulation+exchange+between+Greece+and+Turkey" class="Z3988"></span></span>
