</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20170730211554/http://biblio-archive.unog.ch/Dateien/CouncilMSD/C-524-M-187-1924-II_EN.pdf">"The Settlement of Greek Refugees. Scheme for an International Loan"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. Geneva: League of Nations. 30 October 1924. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://biblio-archive.unog.ch/Dateien/CouncilMSD/C-524-M-187-1924-II_EN.pdf">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> on 30 July 2017<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">16 April</span> 2018</span> &#8211; via scopeArchiv.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Settlement+of+Greek+Refugees.+Scheme+for+an+International+Loan&amp;rft.place=Geneva&amp;rft.pub=League+of+Nations&amp;rft.date=1924-10-30&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbiblio-archive.unog.ch%2FDateien%2FCouncilMSD%2FC-524-M-187-1924-II_EN.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APopulation+exchange+between+Greece+and+Turkey" class="Z3988"></span></span>
